title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 53)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

In keeping with the same theme as our last three bundles, this 53rd offering also contains music previously shared this past month.  Once done, I've got 62 more titles to share which should be good for almost three more bundles.  So hopefully we can seed this one fast amongst ourselves so I can move onto bundle #54.  Any seeding help you may be able to provide would be appreciated.
